        <span class="absolute inset-0 rounded-[2rem] bg-blue-500/20 animate-ping opacity-75"></span>
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 relative z-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"></path></svg>
    </div>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Stok Sedang Dipersiapkan</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Tim kami sedang menyiapkan inventori terbaik untuk kategori <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"><%= categoryName %></strong>. Hubungi admin via Telegram jika Anda membutuhkan request khusus atau kustomisasi server!
    </p>
